MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-124. State ex rel. John Deere Co. v. Bannon.

In Procedendo. This case originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of procedendo. Upon consideration of relator’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective January 26, 1993.

ACCORDINGLY,.IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
